The purpose of '''this guide is to give Ironmen a direct pathway towards bossing''' only, and to do it in as short a time as possible. This guide is Hardcore Ironman friendly, but you may find that some sections take you longer to complete.

=Main guide=

==Part 1: Starting off==
This first section of the guide aims to unlock as many of the repeatable activities as fast as possible. In addition, you will complete a lot of subquests, making the transition into late game quests a lot easier.

You should try and complete the following repeatable activities whenever they are available. It is recommended to add [[notes]] in-game for all of your repeatable tasks.

It is recommended to start each monthly task from when the guide specifies to.
