|- data-rowid = "Hunter 62"
|Train your Hunter to level 62
|'''Method To train Hunter:'''
* Catch [[Swift whirligig]]s at [[Het's Oasis]].
** Collect 50 [[Irises]].
** At one of the Hunter training locations in Het's Oasis, fill one [[Flower basket]] with 32 Irises, fill the second with 15 Irises.
** Handle the crocodile. Catch one of the two [[Plain whirligig]]s in the pool.
** While the crocodile is moving towards the Plain whirligig, chain three Swift whirligigs (may need to spam click).
** After the crocodile deposits the [[Plain whirligig shell]] on the shore, repeat this process with the second Plain whirligig. Do not bother looting the shells.
** The first Plain whirligig will have respawned by the time the crocodile fetches the second one.
** Chaining swift whirligigs doesn't consume any flowers in the flower baskets, but if you accidentally catch one of the swift whirligigs directly (instead of chaining), it will use one of the flowers, and you may eventually need to fetch more.
* This method provides 120-160k XP per hour, without upgrades from [[Dundee's Crocodile Upgrades]], or time to grow irises taken into account.
