==Part 4: Endgame combat training==
This section will conclude your combat training. This section is not a requirement, however is recommended before starting [[Ironman Mode/Strategies/Efficient Ironman Pathway Guide#Part 5: End Game Skilling & Quests|Part 5: End Game Skilling & Quests]] section.
It is recommended that you train using one of the following methods:
* [[Slayer training|Slayer]]
* [[Abyss/Combat training|Abyss combat training]] (Bring [[Underworld Grimoire]] to bank ashes)
* [[Shattered Worlds]]
* [[Contract|Arc contracts]]

'''Note:''' As of April 2026, all [[Aura|auras]] have been removed from the game. For combat sustain during this section, use [[Vampyrism]] from the [[Ancient Magicks]] spellbook (requires 69 {{sc|Magic}}) or [[Penance]] in place of the former Vampyrism and Penance auras.

