| 1
| Solemn Smith I (60 Smithing)
|-
| 2
| Golden Cannon (71 Smithing)
|-
| 3
| Royale Cannon (79 Smithing)
|}
''If you go for 99/110 Smithing, you should purchase unlocks in the following order:''
# [[Blacksmith's outfit]]
